---
// Values section
---

<section id="values">
  <div class="section-container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">What I value</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Principles I<br />lead by</h2>

    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <h3>Inclusivity is non-negotiable</h3>
        <p>Diverse teams build better products. I actively work to create environments where
          everyone feels safe, heard, and empowered to contribute their best ideas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h3>Learn in the open</h3>
        <p>I share what I know and what I don't. Writing, teaching, and making mistakes
          publicly builds trust and accelerates growth for the whole team.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h3>Ship, then iterate</h3>
        <p>Perfection is the enemy of progress. I believe in getting meaningful work into
          users' hands early and improving based on real feedback, not assumptions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <h3>Amplify, don't gatekeep</h3>
        <p>My job is to make the people around me better. I coach, pair, and share context
          so the team grows stronger with every sprint, not more dependent on me.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h3>Simplicity is a feature</h3>
        <p>The best architecture is the one the whole team can understand. I push for
          straightforward solutions over clever abstractions, because maintainability
          outlasts brilliance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h3>Own the outcome, not the ego</h3>
        <p>I care about impact, not credit. Whether a great idea comes from a junior
          developer or a stakeholder, the goal is always the same: build something
          that matters.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
